{"tid":1566083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我屋企冇節做？","createTime":"2019-09-13T11:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:34:33.000Z","uid":157923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adb6103601b131594f5d90e77078f249982f2988","tid":1566083,"uid":157923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"屋企人一向都唔重視一啲儀式野<br />\n除咗新年會去拜年同重陽會去拜山<br />\n其他日子一概不理<br />\n平時食飯大家都分開食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊啲朋友都覺得我好怪<br />\n點解成日都自己一個食<br />\n明明大家都係到<br />\n因為我覺得食野自己一個食都冇問題<br />\n食飯無論係屋企定出面都係一個人既活動<br />\n<br />\n但關係唔係唔好<br />\n只係個個都鐘意自己一個<br />\n<br />\n搞到我自己都有啲唔識點同人地維繫長遠既關係<br />\n因為同屋企人住咁耐個互動都好疏離"},{"pid":"568d96a01233b6a997464a6aa8d23738a05668ac","tid":1566083,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe5fc9db38afa5654f345e6a14c0a9629113a46c","tid":1566083,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnai